      About this item

      • (2.02") 51.3mm AMOLED Display with 750NITS Brightness: Experience vivid and clear visuals on the large 51.3mm always-on AMOLED display with a sharp 240x296 resolution and 750NITS brightness for enhanced clarity under any lighting.
      • Bluetooth Calling & Voice Assistant: Make and receive calls directly from your smartwatch with Bluetooth calling and use the built-in voice assistant to manage tasks hands-free while on the go.
      • 120+ Sports Modes & Activity Tracking: Choose from over 120 sports modes, including running, cycling, and yoga, to monitor your workouts and track your fitness progress with precision.
      • Complete Health Monitoring - SpO2, Heart Rate & Female Health: Track your health effortlessly with SpO2 monitoring, continuous heart rate tracking, and specialized female health features, all available in this advanced smartwatch.
      • Long Battery Life - Up to 7 Days: Enjoy up to 5-7 days of uninterrupted use on a single charge, with a standby time of up to 20 days, keeping you connected without frequent recharging.
      • IP67 Waterproof & Dustproof: Designed for durability, the Fire-Boltt Brillia is IP67 rated, making it resistant to water and dust, perfect for swimming, workouts, and outdoor adventures.
      • Stylish & Comfortable Multiple Strap Colors: Customize your look with a variety of vibrant strap colors, giving you the flexibility to match your style while wearing the Fire-Boltt Brillia smartwatch.
      • Comprehensive Fitness & Wellness Tracking: Monitor calories, steps, sleep quality, and daily activity with advanced sensors, giving you full insights into your wellness journey.
      • Sleek Design & Lightweight Build: With its modern design, large display, and comfortable lightweight feel, this smartwatch is perfect for daily wear, whether at the gym, office, or casual outings.
      • User-Friendly Interface with Touchscreen: Navigate through the features effortlessly with an easy-to-use touchscreen, designed for seamless interactions and quick access to notifications, health data, and more.
